name: Y is for Yen the Yellowfin Tuna
description:
This is the creation of 8 year old NFT artist Big 8 Art.  He does not have a Twitter account but mentor Lily White can be reached @rblbab if you have questions.

Big 8 Art is in the process of creating artwork for every letter of the alphabet. This NFT will be entered into the #HENjackpot event.  Big 8 wants you to know he learned that some people think eating fish on New Year's Eve is good luck!

The fish was hand drawn and then edited on the computer... yes someone found out about the smudge tool.  LOL
